oil firm cut 1987 indonesian explor spend foreign oil compani will spend less on explor in indonesia thi year than last , budget 2.7 billion dlr for calendar 1987 against 1986 spend of 2.8 billion dlr , the state oil compani pertamina said . actual spend last year fell short of the budget figur of 3.2 billion dlr , as oil compani slash expenditur becaus of the crash in world oil price . jumardi jukardi , head of pertamina 's coordin board for foreign contractor , said foreign compani will drill 110 explor well and 431 develop well thi year , against 108 and 330 last year .